<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TMaL38">
<l>mēmporuḷ pōka viṭṭu meymmaiyai mikavu ṇarntu</l>
<l>āmpari caṟintu koṇṭaimpula ṉakatta ṭakki</l>
<l>kāmpuṟat talaici raittuṉ kaṭaittalai yiruntu vāḻuñ</l>
<l>cōmparai yukatti pōluñ cūḻpuṉala raṅkat tāṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O You from Raṅgam surrounded by streams!</l>
<l>You seem to delight in the idlers who live remaining at Your entrance</l>
<l rend="indent">letting go of things that [they] desire,</l>
<l rend="indent">well realising the truth,</l>
<l rend="indent">knowing [their] proper nature,</l>
<l rend="indent">controlling [their] five sense organs from within</l>
<l rend="indent">[and] cutting off the [burden from the] head</l>
<l rend="indent">So that the [whole] stalks are severed.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
